title: Vintage Victoria
abstract: A look at aspects of life across Victoria between 1940 and the mid 1960s.
description: The early years of the Healesville Sanctuary in the 1940s, initial concerns over High Plains soil erosion, a day at the show in the 1950s, and a tour of Victoria's early festivals and tourism 'hotspots'.  Presented here are a range of films showing the development of Victoria in the early post-war decades.
